a.) cannot attend certain raids at this point due to missing these two encounters<br>
b.)and even if i could attend, I would not even receive the flag for the current encounter since I didnt have the <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>previous</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> one!<br>
